378
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:12,000
Have you forgotten?

379
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,640
On your first day back to the Capital,

380
00:24:15,110 --> 00:24:17,250
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)
the first person you met

381
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:19,400
was me.

382
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:22,480
Actually, since that day,

383
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:25,750
I've found my mother.

384
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:29,590
I don't want to lose you again.

385
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:33,270
Even though you didn't raise me,

386
00:24:33,590 --> 00:24:36,400
we have a future together.

387
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:39,550
You can be with me as I grow up.

388
00:24:39,790 --> 00:24:40,630
Besides,

389
00:24:40,790 --> 00:24:43,070
didn't we agree?

390
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,240
We are both

391
00:24:44,550 --> 00:24:47,110
children without mothers.

392
00:24:47,110 --> 00:24:49,350
When we miss our mother,

393
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:52,350
I can hug you,

394
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:57,400
and you can hug me.

395
00:24:57,830 --> 00:25:00,400
If you miss your mother,

396
00:25:00,830 --> 00:25:02,680
just hold me instead,

397
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:04,790
okay?

398
00:25:05,090 --> 00:25:08,230
♪A cold heart beats in silence♪

399
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:13,160
You found me in hide and seek.

400
00:25:13,590 --> 00:25:17,240
This is my gift for you.

401
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:20,240
Last year on my birthday,

402
00:25:20,310 --> 00:25:24,030
I ran into Grandmother's yard,

403
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:27,240
and she gave me this.

404
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:31,060
Your name is engraved on it.

405
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:34,040
♪Snow falls in silence♪

406
00:25:34,300 --> 00:25:37,180
♪I love you in silence♪

407
00:25:37,860 --> 00:25:39,380
♪If hatred never fades♪

408
