♪Sleepless nights linger on♪

428
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:41,820
(Light, Fu Residence)

429
00:26:42,540 --> 00:26:44,940
♪Falling asleep together♪

430
00:26:44,940 --> 00:26:49,220
♪At this moment, you are by my side♪

431
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:52,240
♪Watching the moon♪

432
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:53,110
Mrs. Fu.

433
00:26:54,110 --> 00:26:55,270
Is Lingzhi sleeping?

434
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,240
Yes.

435
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:00,960
Mrs. Fu, I need

436
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,070
to apologize to you.

437
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,070
For what?

438
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:05,520
Just not long ago,

439
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,070
at the Nanshan Clinic.

440
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,880
I did see you there.

441
00:27:08,880 --> 00:27:10,160
That's why I spoke so much.

442
00:27:10,590 --> 00:27:12,110
But Mr. Fu truly didn't see you.

443
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:14,590
His words were heartfelt.

444
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:16,000
It's all my fault.

445
00:27:16,310 --> 00:27:17,550
I messed things up.

446
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,550
He really didn't know?

447
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:21,640
Hasn't he explained it to you yet?

448
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:24,550
He was demoted and punished

449
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:26,400
for your sake.

450
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:29,000
Zhuang Shiyang told me

451
00:27:30,350 --> 00:27:32,720
Fu Yunxi was forced by him.

452
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,830
You believe Zhuang Shiyang's words?

453
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,480
I saw it with my own eyes.

454
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,000
After you fainted,

455
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:39,920
Mr. Fu carried you inside.

456
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:42,200
He sat by your side for a long time

457
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:43,720
before deciding to abandon

458
00:27:44,030 --> 00:27:45,750
all his previous plans for you.

459
00:27:46,450 --> 00:27:47,370
Later that night,

460
00:27:47,380 --> 00:27:49,160
Zhuang Shiyang used this against him.

461
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:51,200
He mentioned it,

462
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:55,070
but I didn't believe it then.

463
00:27:56,110 --> 00:27:57,480
I, Mu Feng, swear to the heavens,

464
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:01,070
though Mr. Fu is a bit

465
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,560
ruthless and cunning,

466
00:28:03,110 --> 00:28:04,430
using any means to achieve goals,

467
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:07,000
his feelings for you are genuine.

468
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:08,430
If I'm lying,

469
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:10,030
may I never marry

470
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:11,560
and be single forever.

471
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:19,510
I knew all along.

472
00:28:21,480 --> 00:28:22,960
I was using his sincerity

473
00:28:26,550 --> 00:28:28,070
to my advantage.

474
00:28:54,350 --> 00:28:55,190
Does it hurt?

475
00:28:56,070 --> 00:28:57,110
Why don't you try?

476
00:29:27,350 --> 00:29:28,310
Zhuang Shiyang.

477
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,350
I'll never let this go.

478
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:36,680
Now there's another blood feud.

479
00:29:37,720 --> 00:29:39,200
All these matters

480
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,110
stem from Zhuang Shiyang.

481
00:29:42,550 --> 00:29:44,030
I will never let him go.

482
00:29:44,830 --> 00:29:46,960
His crimes are countless,
and he deserves to die.

483
00:29:47,270 --> 00:29:48,680
But no matter how he dies,

484
00:29:49,270 --> 00:29:50,290
I don't want it to be you,

485
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:52,030
sneaking in under the cover of night

486
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:54,680
and assassinating him.

487
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:56,760
Why?

488
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:57,910
Don't forget,

489
00:29:58,110 --> 00:29:59,750
our marriage is a deal.

490
00:29:59,920 --> 00:30:01,310
My help comes with conditions.

491
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:03,270
You promised me

492
00:30:03,550 --> 00:30:05,270
to care for the Fu Family.

493
00:30:05,550 --> 00:30:06,390
I don't get it.

494
00:30:07,200 --> 00:30:08,920
Why insist on this?

495
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:11,880
You can protect them yourself.

496
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,000
Just remember,

497
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:15,070
a deal is a deal.

498
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,750
We must keep our word.

499
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:21,240
Fine. I promise you.

500
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,720
You deceived me,

501
00:30:24,830 --> 00:30:26,110
and I deceived you.

502
00:30:27,550 --> 00:30:29,240
But this time, I swear,

503
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:32,000
I'm being sincere.

504
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,640
You always say

505
00:30:39,200 --> 00:30:40,350
you want a home.

506
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:43,550
What do you think a home is?

507
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:45,520
At least,

508
00:30:46,480 --> 00:30:48,270
a home must

509
00:30:49,790 --> 00:30:51,070
have blood relatives.

510
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:56,270
Like you with Lady Qiu and Aunt Kou.

511
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:04,640
You don't know this,

512
00:31:06,750 --> 00:31:09,240
but I have no blood ties to them.

513
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:12,960
I'm their adopted son.

514
00:31:16,350 --> 00:31:18,510
My parents died in war.

515
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:21,240
I'm just an orphan.

516
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,000
Yet with love and care,

517
00:31:25,590 --> 00:31:26,830
this is my home.

518
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:29,590
And it can

519
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,030
be your home, too.

520
00:31:47,110 --> 00:31:48,070
Yunxi.

521
00:31:57,070 --> 00:31:58,350
- Hanyan.
- Mother.

522
00:32:00,030 --> 00:32:01,480
- Yunxi.
- Mother.

523
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:02,960
Have you heard

524
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:05,350
Noble Consort Miao was executed?

525
00:32:06,640 --> 00:32:09,000
We've been close to her lately.

526
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,720
Could this bring us trouble?

527
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:13,160
Don't worry, Mother.

528
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,680
Though we were acquainted with her,

529
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:18,110
we won't be implicated.

530
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:20,160
Besides, His Majesty has decreed

531
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,590
that the matter will not

532
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:22,710
be pursued any further.

533
00:32:24,350 --> 00:32:26,220
That's good.

534
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:28,830
I worry about you.

535
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:30,430
Yunxi,

536
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:32,390
Hanyan,

537
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:35,030
being together as a family

538
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:37,270
is our true blessing.

539
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:40,110
I'm afraid

540
00:32:40,830 --> 00:32:43,480
of any harm befalling you.

541
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:45,110
I…

542
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:46,840
Rest assured.

543
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:49,270
We'll be fine.

544
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:53,270
But you and Aunt Kou

545
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:55,350
should stay home these days.

546
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:56,880
Try not to go out.

547
00:32:58,270 --> 00:32:59,110
I understand.

548
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:02,240
We were once admired,

549
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:05,240
but now feared by all.

550
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:09,240
You're worried about us being shunned.

551
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:10,800
I know.

552
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:14,110
It's getting late.

553
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:16,480
Let me take you to rest, Mother.

554
00:33:16,790 --> 00:33:17,630
Alright.

555
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:19,110
Mother.

556
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:20,560
Let's go.

557
00:33:38,400 --> 00:33:39,400
You're still injured.

558
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:41,720
Go get some rest.

559
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,520
It's alright.

560
00:33:52,110 --> 00:33:53,830
They were once the Capital's belles.

561
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:58,030
One married into an officials,

562
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:01,790
the other into the palace.

563
00:34:02,550 --> 00:34:04,350
Yet in the end, they both met the same fate.

564
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:06,920
History will record

565
00:34:07,550 --> 00:34:08,630
another treacherous consort,

566
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:11,110
eternally condemned for ruining the nation.

567
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:15,030
A life so fragile

568
00:34:16,360 --> 00:34:17,840
vanishes without a trace.

569
00:34:19,030 --> 00:34:20,550
The so-called noble lady…

570
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:27,150
How pathetic.

571
00:34:31,400 --> 00:34:32,960
Just now, Mu Feng told me

572
00:34:33,510 --> 00:34:35,320
Mu Yan has made some progress

573
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:37,060
on Yuwen Chang'an's sandalwood box.

574
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:40,000
What progress?

575
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:42,000
Noble Consort Miao's matter was sudden.

576
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:44,190
I haven't met with Mu Yan yet.

577
00:34:44,700 --> 00:34:46,280
I'll go to the Judicial Review tomorrow.

578
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,880
Wait at home for my message.

579
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,920
I hope Mr. Yuwen

580
00:34:52,280 --> 00:34:53,760
won't let us down.

581
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:57,320
(Hanlin Academy)
Congratulations, Mr. Zhuang.

582
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:59,480
After all these years
at the Hanlin Academy,

583
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:01,030
you have finally made it.

584
00:35:01,510 --> 00:35:02,350
Indeed.

585
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:05,400
Mr. Zhuang has been hardworking.

586
00:35:05,550 --> 00:35:08,000
(Endless Learning)
Now he's achieved great success.

587
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:10,120
Promoted from a seventh-rank
junior compiler

588
00:35:10,150 --> 00:35:12,670
to a fifth-rank academician.

589
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:14,840
Granted personally by His Majesty.

590
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:17,070
This grand honor should be recorded

591
00:35:17,110 --> 00:35:18,510
in the family genealogy.

592
00:35:18,520 --> 00:35:19,420
Yes, indeed.

593
00:35:19,430 --> 00:35:21,000
Perhaps in a few years,

594
00:35:21,110 --> 00:35:24,280
Mr. Zhuang might join the Grand Secretariat.

595
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,640
Please.

596
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:26,760
Congratulations.

597
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:27,800
- Please.
- Congrats.

598
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:28,680
That's flattering.

599
00:35:28,690 --> 00:35:30,550
I possess no special skills,

600
00:35:30,670 --> 00:35:32,280
just some simple craftsmanship.

601
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:33,760
Today's promotion

602
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:35,800
is a blessing.

603
00:35:36,150 --> 00:35:39,320
I dare not compare myself to you

604
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,480
esteemed scholars.

605
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,590
Mr. Zhuang, you're too modest.

606
00:35:43,690 --> 00:35:44,840
- Too humble.
- Too modest.

607
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:45,920
Truly too humble.

608
00:35:54,230 --> 00:35:56,590
Even though Consort Miao has fallen,

609
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,800
Fu Yunxi and Zhuang Hanyan

610
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,230
managed to escape.

611
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:06,190
So frustrating.

612
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:15,070
Sir,

613
00:36:15,470 --> 00:36:17,030
I have a plan.

614
00:36:26,230 --> 00:36:28,280
A woman should know her place.

615
00:36:28,630 --> 00:36:30,070
This is not your concern.

616
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:34,550
Yingyue would never overstep her bounds.

617
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,030
You're right.

618
00:36:42,710 --> 00:36:44,280
I will remember this.

619
00:36:45,030 --> 00:36:47,280
My grandmother's 60th birthday
is in two days.

620
00:36:47,550 --> 00:36:50,070
Could you join our celebration?

621
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:50,910
I don't have time.

622
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,230
Go on your own.

623
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:54,960
Just four hours allowed.

624
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:03,940
(Judicial Review)

625
00:37:03,960 --> 00:37:05,360
Mu Feng mentioned progress here.

626
00:37:05,800 --> 00:37:06,640
Yes.

627
00:37:07,070 --> 00:37:08,840
And it's at the Department of Supervision.

628
00:37:09,510 --> 00:37:10,560
Department of Supervision?

629
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,920
It's been searched twice before,

630
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:14,400
but found no trace.

631
00:37:14,550 --> 00:37:15,590
Last time we were there,

632
00:37:15,590 --> 00:37:17,270
we focused on the offices and archives,

633
00:37:17,290 --> 00:37:18,840
where documents are storage.

634
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:19,880
But we overlooked

635
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:21,280
Mr. Yuwen's connections.

636
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:22,840
Where's the clue?

637
00:37:22,960 --> 00:37:23,800
The morgue.

638
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:29,590
(Morgue)
We reek of corpses.

639
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:32,030
(Serving Justice)
We're the least welcomed.

640
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,120
In the Department of Supervision,

641
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:36,550
only Mr. Yuwen treats me well.

642
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:39,400
We share the same plight.

643
00:37:39,960 --> 00:37:42,630
Neither of us ever married.

644
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,670
Over time, we grew closer.

645
00:37:46,800 --> 00:37:47,880
About five or six years ago,

646
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:50,590
he entrusted this box to me.

647
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:51,840
He said it's quiet here,

648
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,510
more dead than living,

649
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:54,670
which makes it safer.

650
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:57,400
Sometimes he would take it for days

651
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,920
(Coroner Sun)
and soon return it.

652
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:01,510
He never told me

653
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:02,920
what was inside.

654
00:38:03,230 --> 00:38:04,630
Yet, every time he returned it,

655
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:06,670
it felt heavier.

656
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:08,590
When Mr. Yuwen left the Capital,

657
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:10,320
why didn't he take it?

658
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,000
He left in a hurry,

659
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:15,030
and had someone send me a message.

660
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,590
It was poetic,

661
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:19,880
saying it was a box of sorrowful tears,

662
00:38:20,030 --> 00:38:21,590
unfit for the land of bliss.

663
00:38:21,670 --> 00:38:23,110
He asked me to keep it safe,

664
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,510
as it might be useful someday.

665
00:38:28,070 --> 00:38:28,910
Mr. Fu, you...

666
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:38,980
(Archived Documents)

667
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:44,300
(Zhuang's Ancestral Hall in Danzhou)

668
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,970
(Zhuang Shiyang looks terrified)
These are

669
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:47,480
Mr. Yuwen's manuscripts.

670
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:49,190
According to what he wrote,

671
00:38:50,630 --> 00:38:51,550
three years ago,

672
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:54,190
he entrusted you
with something very important.

673
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:55,640
Mr. Fu,

674
00:38:56,110 --> 00:38:57,670
did Mr. Yuwen truly

675
00:38:58,030 --> 00:38:59,320
send you to retrieve it?

676
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:01,360
Mr. Yuwen has passed away.

677
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:03,510
Perhaps these items

678
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:05,510
are his chance for justice.

679
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:08,230
You mean, Mr. Yuwen is…

680
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,160
Mrs. Fu.

681
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:21,950
Did he find it?

682
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:23,100
Mr. Fu didn't explain much.

683
00:39:23,120 --> 00:39:24,760
He asked you to go to the Department.

684
00:39:25,760 --> 00:39:27,230
Alright. Let's go.

685
00:39:28,220 --> 00:39:35,220
(Sealed)

686
00:40:02,620 --> 00:40:05,660
(Department of Supervision)

687
00:40:31,260 --> 00:40:37,460
(Serving Justice)

688
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:12,760
It's poisonous.

689
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:16,030
Whose remains

690
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:18,280
are these?

691
00:41:21,190 --> 00:41:22,150
Your grandfather,

692
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:24,190
Zhuang Hanliang.

693
00:41:56,091 --> 00:41:58,901
♪She hides away her past♪

694
00:41:59,181 --> 00:42:01,511
♪Covered in scars♪

695
00:42:03,861 --> 00:42:06,621
♪She forgets who she is♪

696
00:42:06,991 --> 00:42:09,251
♪Disguised as one returning home♪

697
00:42:10,611 --> 00:42:13,951
♪When night falls, in the yard♪

698
00:42:13,951 --> 00:42:16,891
♪Mist rises in swirls♪

699
00:42:18,351 --> 00:42:21,521
♪She steps onto the battlefield♪

700
00:42:21,801 --> 00:42:25,621
♪No distraction is allowed♪

701
00:42:26,961 --> 00:42:30,021
♪A touch of love, a trace of hate♪

702
00:42:30,281 --> 00:42:32,791
♪No need to question♪

703
00:42:34,681 --> 00:42:37,661
♪The truth and falsehood♪

704
00:42:37,661 --> 00:42:40,751
♪Needs to be discerned♪

705
00:42:41,511 --> 00:42:44,851
♪Seeking warmth in peril♪

706
00:42:44,851 --> 00:42:49,191
♪Only to be mocked as naive♪

707
00:42:49,311 --> 00:42:52,661
♪War drums sound, beacons flare♪

708
00:42:52,661 --> 00:42:56,531
♪Who can break free♪

709
00:42:56,971 --> 00:42:59,431
♪She is willing to become a blade♪

710
00:42:59,431 --> 00:43:01,381
♪Moving forward without retreat♪

711
00:43:01,381 --> 00:43:04,661
♪Charging into this lonely fortress♪

712
00:43:04,661 --> 00:43:07,231
♪Even in a fateful clash♪

713
00:43:07,231 --> 00:43:09,051
♪With eyes stained with blood♪

714
00:43:09,051 --> 00:43:12,301
♪She holds no grudge♪

715
00:43:12,511 --> 00:43:14,871
♪She does not trust fate♪

716
00:43:14,871 --> 00:43:16,911
♪She does not pray to gods♪

717
00:43:16,911 --> 00:43:20,101
♪She grips the blade♪

718
00:43:20,231 --> 00:43:22,701
♪As geese fly south in winter♪

719
00:43:22,701 --> 00:43:24,621
♪She alone journeys north♪

720
00:43:24,621 --> 00:43:31,611
♪Seeking truth in falsehood♪

721
00:43:32,181 --> 00:43:34,461
♪She'd become the blade♪

722
00:43:34,661 --> 00:43:36,431
♪With love as her shield♪

723
00:43:36,431 --> 00:43:39,731
♪Plunging into this mortal world♪

724
00:43:39,931 --> 00:43:42,311
♪Shattering mirages♪

725
00:43:42,311 --> 00:43:44,161
♪And illusions♪

726
00:43:44,161 --> 00:43:47,641
♪To pay respect to the fallen souls♪

727
00:43:47,641 --> 00:43:49,891
♪She does not trust fate♪

728
00:43:49,891 --> 00:43:51,941
♪She does not pray to gods♪

729
00:43:51,941 --> 00:43:55,341
♪She grips the blade♪

730
00:43:55,341 --> 00:43:57,711
♪As geese fly south in winter♪

731
00:43:57,711 --> 00:43:59,811
♪She alone journeys north♪

732
00:43:59,811 --> 00:44:05,691
♪Seeking only a trace♪

733
00:44:06,771 --> 00:44:10,251
♪Of warmth♪

